title: UberMenu v3.2.0.2 - Premium WordPress Plugins
description:
UberMenu is a user-friendly, highly customizable, responsive Mega Menu WordPress plugin. It works out of the box with the WordPress 3 Menu System, making it simple to get started but powerful enough to create highly customized and creative mega menu configurations. Contains external links.

To install:
1. Upload the folder to the /wp-content/plugins/ directory
2. Activate the plugin through the 'Plugins' menu in WordPress
